  </section>

  <!-- Problem & Solution -->
  <section class="build-bring" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" data-reveal>
        <span class="section-tag">Two paths, one platform</span>
        <h2>Build your AI workforce<br><span class="gradient-text">or bring your own</span></h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Whether you start from scratch or import your existing setup, Vutler gives you full control.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bb-grid">
        <div class="bb-card bb-build" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
          <div class="bb-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g transform="translate(32,32)" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"><path d="M0,-26 L-22,-10 L-14,20 L14,20 L22,-10 Z"/><line x1="0" y1="-26" x2="-14" y2="20"/><line x1="0" y1="-26" x2="14" y2="20"/><line x1="-22" y1="-10" x2="14" y2="20"/><line x1="22" y1="-10" x2="-14" y2="20"/><line x1="0" y1="28" x2="-14" y2="20"/><line x1="0" y1="28" x2="14" y2="20"/><line x1="0" y1="28" x2="-22" y2="-10"/><line x1="0" y1="28" x2="22" y2="-10"/><line x1="-22" y1="-10" x2="22" y2="-10"/></g></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Build</h3>
          <p>Start from proven agent templates. Customize prompts, tools, and workflows. Deploy in minutes — no infra needed.</p>
          <ul class="bb-list">
            <li><span class="bb-check"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> Customer support agent</li>
            <li><span class="bb-check"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> Sales assistant</li>
            <li><span class="bb-check"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> Data pipeline agent</li>
            <li><span class="bb-check"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> Custom system prompts</li>
            <li><span class="bb-check"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> Deploy in 1 click</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#get-started" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Templates →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bb-divider">
          <span class="bb-or">or</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bb-card bb-bring" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
          <div class="bb-icon-wrap bb-icon-purple">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Bring</h3>
          <p>Import your existing agents, connect your infrastructure, and manage everything from one unified dashboard.</p>
          <ul class="bb-list">
            <li><span class="bb-check bb-check-purple"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> Import existing agents</li>
            <li><span class="bb-check bb-check-purple"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> BYOKEY (OpenAI, Anthropic…)</li>
            <li><span class="bb-check bb-check-purple"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> Full REST API access</li>
            <li><span class="bb-check bb-check-purple"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> Custom integrations</li>
            <li><span class="bb-check bb-check-purple"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8.5L6.5 12L13 4"/></svg></span> On-premise option</li>
